### Variables

@baseUrl = localhost:3000/dev

@contentType = application/json



# basic request
http://{{baseUrl}}


### Get all Emails
GET http://{{baseUrl}}/api/emails


### Get one Email
GET http://{{baseUrl}}/api/emails/{{emailId}}


### Create a new Email
# @name createEmail
POST http://{{baseUrl}}/api/emails
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "subject": "Learn the Nest from post man 3",
    "reciever": "Lanzruizdesigns@gmail.com",
    "message": "Complete the NestJS course",
    "status": "NOT_SENT"
}

### Set the task id
@emailId = {{createEmail.response.body.id}}

### update a Email

PATCH http://{{baseUrl}}/api/emails/{{emailId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "status": "SENT"
}

 
### Delete a Email

Delete http://{{baseUrl}}/api/email/{{emailId}}
 
 


